profile:
At Hometurf Lawn Care, we have been treating the lawns of our loyal customers for over 30 years. As a family-owned and -operated business, we have grown by delivering lush, healthy, green lawns while using only the highest quality products applied by professional lawn care technicians. Let us help you make your lawn look its best this season!

Our season-long lawn care programs take the guess work out of which products to use and when. Applications are scheduled to be applied four to six weeks apart throughout the season for optimal turf care. We strive to ensure everything your lawn needs is included in our programs. No telemarketing or sales calls pushing unnecessary extras.

Our services include: lawn care programs, lawn maintenance programs, fertilizer, weed control, insect control, aeration, grass seeding, dethatching, top dressing, chinch bug control and grub control.

profile:
Paramount Landscaping started with the idea that customer service should be a priority in our industry. The vision was to create a white collar company in a blue collar world; one that harvests accountability, professionalism, customer care and knowledge into an industry that pays very little attention to these important words.
The company started in 2005 with one man’s dream to build this vision. In only twelve short years it has grown to one of the premier landscaping companies in the GTA, continually winning the Reader’s Choice Awards in Burlington, Oakville and Flamborough and recently winning the prestigious Consumer Choice Award in Hamilton and Niagara regions for Best Landscape Contractor.

As the company built, so did our teams’ qualifications and specialties. This meant our range of services expanded as well.Paramount now has a senior management team of seven people with over 80 years’ experience in landscaping industry. We service 26 cities and we specialize not only in property maintenance and landscape construction, but 16 other accompanying trades as well. We have a true desire for creating beautifully manicured properties and stunning outdoor retreats. We would love to share our passion with you.
